      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The exterior exhibits significant cosmetic issues, including several large dents, widespread paint oxidation, and deep scratches across multiple panels. Mechanically, the car requires immediate professional attention as it struggles to maintain a steady idle and has several fluid leaks. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, making this a significant undertaking for any restorer.",
